{"tid":1177550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"細個同爸爸試部對講機調錯頻，人地以為撞鬼","createTime":"2019-05-29T22:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T20:28:59.000Z","uid":191988,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ddb08ca06164e27f5b7fd3a8c4a724bc21815d96","tid":1177550,"uid":191988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T22:28:27.000Z","msg":"我爸爸番工需要用到對講機<br />\n記得好細個小學既時候<br />\n因為爸爸公司部對講機需要維修<br />\n佢就拎左2部番屋企整<br />\n爸爸叫我拎住其中一部對講機<br />\n出廳同佢講下野做testing<br />\n本身好地地，得我同爸爸講野<br />\n之後出現多2把男人聲<br />\n我就對住部對講機講<br />\n「爸爸，爸爸，係咪你呀？」<br />\n之後其中一個男人講...<br />\n「哇，聽唔聽到，好撚驚呀喂」<br />\n我爸爸即刻衝出廳熄左我部機<br />\n之後爸爸笑到pk<br />\n話佢唔小心調頻調左去其他人個台<br />\n佢地可能以為撞鬼<br />\n我當時重係細路女聲<br />\n人地無啦啦我叫爸爸<br />\n都咪話唔驚～"},{"pid":"e75f8a5d47c81f42ac847523ea3cea49c3467bb6","tid":1177550,"uid":167032,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T22:29:39.000Z","msg":"我而家知便啲鬼故點來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5b9367516921f17014a3d32f295e4e4e863dd6","tid":1177550,"uid":191988,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"e75f8a5d47c81f42ac847523ea3cea49c3467bb6","tid":1177550,"uid":167032,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T22:29:39.000Z","msg":"我而家知便啲鬼故點來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T22:31:00.000Z","msg":"可能成為左個2個男人既鬼故<br />\n嚇親人哋，諗返起都唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76229f8faaf45ef49d2e5a6ed00249ef8fcb16a9","tid":1177550,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da5b9367516921f17014a3d32f295e4e4e863dd6","tid":1177550,"uid":191988,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"e75f8a5d47c81f42ac847523ea3cea49c3467bb6","tid":1177550,"uid":167032,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T22:29:39.000Z","msg":"我而家知便啲鬼故點來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-